    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beach Outlet Simulator</strong> 是一款第一人称模拟游戏，你将经营一家零售公司。将你的小店发展成一家大型零售企业。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>商店管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以时尚和实用的方式设计你的商店。充分利用空间展示产品，为顾客提供愉快的购物体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/eb4cbdc3e2a0d521789b2857a22af4e2.poster.avif?t=1761691263\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/eb4cbdc3e2a0d521789b2857a22af4e2.webm?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/eb4cbdc3e2a0d521789b2857a22af4e2.mp4?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 清洁</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顾客很在意商店的整洁。窗户要干净，地板上不能有垃圾！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/39d07f06c7950c0c090e6870adf4c708.poster.avif?t=1761691263\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/39d07f06c7950c0c090e6870adf4c708.webm?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/39d07f06c7950c0c090e6870adf4c708.mp4?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 产品订购</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用专用电脑订购产品和货架！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/f257a45414108924a62dff4b1419508f.poster.avif?t=1761691263\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/f257a45414108924a62dff4b1419508f.webm?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/f257a45414108924a62dff4b1419508f.mp4?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 收银管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >服务速度要快，以满足顾客需求！注意顾客的满意度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/14bf433dde1c6d03feb798bf217af613.poster.avif?t=1761691263\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/14bf433dde1c6d03feb798bf217af613.webm?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/14bf433dde1c6d03feb798bf217af613.mp4?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 业务扩展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用赚到的钱购买新产品，扩展和装饰你的商店。顾客喜欢新鲜感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/b882e8522b76aab952cb8380179eae73.poster.avif?t=1761691263\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/b882e8522b76aab952cb8380179eae73.webm?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/b882e8522b76aab952cb8380179eae73.mp4?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>额外活动</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了经营？你可以玩水上摩托车、滑板车或滑板，甚至可以打篮球！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/a8395102b0dfe260c2117fa33db77404.poster.avif?t=1761691263\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/a8395102b0dfe260c2117fa33db77404.webm?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321090/extras/a8395102b0dfe260c2117fa33db77404.mp4?t=1761691263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
